node.text:
Gillian Anderson and Gabriela Hearst attended the 2021 Met Gala at the @metmuseum in celebration of In America: A Lexicon of Fashion and the 75th anniversary of the #CostumeInstitute. 

Both in Chloé, Gillian wore a made-to-measure dress in repurposed, organic silk crepe with an ammonite nautilus shell – seamlessly integrated by hand-knotted macramé techniques – at its centre. Gabriela wore a chalk white nappa leather dress with perforated scallops from the #ChloeAW21 show.

#MetGala #MetInAmerica
